responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "1AFEDE2B432F8E46408875AB1028D807", "Oh sure it\'s a pretty flower petal, but if I talk, I won\'t be living here no longer. I can\'t risk my life for every penny you see. Even you folk can understand how much we treasure our little camp. You better talk to Dottie, she might be willing to take the risk. You\'ll find her at the green tent in the Northwest campsite.")
